Package: jdiskmark
Version: [[version]]
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
# Requires Java 21+. Java 25 is preferred for full feature support.
# The fat jar bundles all library deps; only a JRE is needed at runtime.
Depends: default-jre | openjdk-25-jre | openjdk-21-jre
Maintainer: JDiskMark Maintainers <maintainers@jdiskmark.net>
Description: JDiskMark - Java Disk Benchmark Utility
 JDiskMark is a cross-platform disk benchmark utility written in Java.
 It measures the sequential read and write performance of storage devices
 and logs results over time for comparison.
